### List all reconciliations (default: 20 most recent)
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations

### List reconciliations filtered by status - matched
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=matched

### List reconciliations filtered by status - matched_with_fee
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=matched_with_fee

### List reconciliations filtered by status - amount_mismatch
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=amount_mismatch

### List reconciliations filtered by status - missing_internal
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=missing_internal

### List reconciliations filtered by status - missing_external
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=missing_external

### List reconciliations filtered by status - duplicate
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?status=duplicate

### List reconciliations with pagination (page 2)
GET http://localhost:8000/reconciliations?limit=10&offset=10

### Run reconciliation engine
POST http://localhost:8000/reconciliations/run
Content-Type: application/json
